import React from 'react'
import {
    MDBInput,
    MDBCol,
    MDBRow,
    MDBContainer,
    MDBCheckbox,
    MDBBtn,
    MDBIcon
} from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <MDBContainer className='mt-5 mb-5 col-10 col-sm-8 col-md-6 col-lg-5'>
        <form>
            <MDBInput className='mb-4 shadow-3' type='email' label='Email Address' />
            <MDBInput className='mb-4 shadow-3' type='password' label='Password' />

            <MDBRow className='mb-4'>
                <MDBCol className='d-flex justify-content-center'>
                    <MDBCheckbox label='Remember me' />
                </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>

            <MDBBtn color='dark' className='mb-4' block><MDBIcon icon='code' fas /> Login</MDBBtn>
        </form>
    </MDBContainer>
  )
}

export default Login
